# Purpose of this software is to flash / install any ISO image of os to portable storage device or make that bootable.

Steps to Install Etcher On ubuntu 

1. download Ether from it's official website https://etcher.balena.io/#download-etcher
2. sudo apt install libfuse2                                                                         # Supporting files required 
3. Extract downloaded files to the directory
4. Change the File permission to executable clicking right button + properties + permissions + allow executing files as a programs 
5. Right click and Run the program file.
